wers recorded.\"}\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between\">\n            <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/30\">MATURITY SEGMENTS</span>\n            <Link href=\"/build/assessment\" className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-white hover:text-[#00FF9D] transition flex items-center gap-1\">\n              <span>{workspace.assessment ? \"RESUME\" : \"START\"}</span>\n              <span>→</span>\n            </Link>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Card 3: ROI Calculator */}\n        <div className={`p-4 rounded-xl border flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[140px] transition-all ${workspace.roi ? \"border-[#E4000F]/30 bg-[#E4000F]/5\" : \"border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01]\"}`}>\n          <div>\n            <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-2\">\n              <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold text-[#E4000F] uppercase\">3. ROI Calculator</span>\n              <span className={`text-[8px] font-mono px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded ${workspace.roi ? \"bg-[#E4000F]/20 text-white\" : \"bg-white/5 text-white/40\"}`}>\n                {workspace.roi ? \"CONFIGURED\" : \"EMPTY\"}\n              </span>\n            </div>\n            <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white mt-3\">Savings Model</h4>\n            <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 font-light mt-1 min-h-[30px] line-clamp-2\">\n              {workspace.roi ? `Sovereign TCO for ${workspace.roi.companySize}. Baseline: $${(workspace.roi.annualCostBaseline / 1000000).toFixed(1)}M/yr.` : \"No economic variables modeled.\"}\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between\">\n            <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/30\">TCO CALCULATIONS</span>\n            <Link href=\"/build/roi\" className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-white hover:text-[#E4000F] transition flex items-center gap-1\">\n              <span>{workspace.roi ? \"RESUME\" : \"START\"}</span>\n              <span>→</span>\n            </Link>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Card 4: Proposal Studio */}\n        <div className={`p-4 rounded-xl border flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[140px] transition-all ${workspace.proposal ? \"border-[#3B82F6]/30 bg-[#3B82F6]/5\" : \"border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01]\"}`}>\n          <div>\n            <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-2\">\n              <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold text-[#3B82F6] uppercase\">4. Proposal Studio</span>\n              <span className={`text-[8px] font-mono px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded ${workspace.proposal ? \"bg-[#3B82F6]/20 text-white\" : \"bg-white/5 text-white/40\"}`}>\n                {workspace.proposal ? \"CONFIGURED\" : \"EMPTY\"}\n              </span>\n            </div>\n            <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white mt-3\">SOW Specifications</h4>\n            <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 font-light mt-1 min-h-[30px] line-clamp-2\">\n              {workspace.proposal ? `Draft Statement of Work for ${workspace.proposal.companyName || \"unnamed company\"}.` : \"No proposal metadata compiled.\"}\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between\">\n            <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/30\">scoping files</span>\n            <Link href=\"/build/proposal\" className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-white hover:text-[#3B82F6] transition flex items-center gap-1\">\n              <span>{workspace.proposal ? \"RESUME\" : \"START\"}</span>\n              <span>→</span>\n            </Link>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Card 5: Talk to Agent */}\n        <div className={`p-4 rounded-xl border flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[140px] transition-all ${workspace.talk ? \"border-[#00FF9D]/30 bg-[#00FF9D]/5\" : \"border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01]\"}`}>\n          <div>\n            <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-2\">\n              <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold text-[#00FF9D] uppercase\">5. Talk to Agent</span>\n              <span className={`text-[8px] font-mono px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded ${workspace.talk ? \"bg-[#00FF9D]/20 text-white\" : \"bg-white/5 text-white/40\"}`}>\n                {workspace.talk ? \"CONFIGURED\" : \"EMPTY\"}\n              </span>\n            </div>\n            <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white mt-3\">Intake Mapping</h4>\n            <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 font-light mt-1 min-h-[30px] line-clamp-2\">\n              {workspace.talk ? `Sync intake saved. Primary Challenge: ${workspace.talk.data?.urgency || \"Compliance Audit\"}` : \"No agentic conversations saved.\"}\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between\">\n            <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/30\">CHAT INTELLIGENCE</span>\n            <Link href=\"/build/talk\" className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-white hover:text-[#00FF9D] transition flex items-center gap-1\">\n              <span>{workspace.talk ? \"RESUME\" : \"START\"}</span>\n              <span>→</span>\n            </Link>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Card 6: Execution Sandbox */}\n        <div className={`p-4 rounded-xl border flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[140px] transition-all ${workspace.sandbox ? \"border-[#009DFF]/30 bg-[#009DFF]/5\" : \"border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01]\"}`}>\n          <div>\n            <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-2\">\n              <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold text-[#009DFF] uppercase\">6. Execution Sandbox</span>\n              <span className={`text-[8px] font-mono px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded ${workspace.sandbox ? \"bg-[#009DFF]/20 text-white\" : \"bg-white/5 text-white/40\"}`}>\n                {workspace.sandbox ? \"CONFIGURED\" : \"EMPTY\"}\n              </span>\n            </div>\n            <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white mt-3\">Simulation Spec</h4>\n            <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 font-light mt-1 min-h-[30px] line-clamp-2\">\n              {workspace.sandbox ? `Active agent: ${workspace.sandbox.activeAgentId}. Category: ${workspace.sandbox.selectedFunction}.` : \"No simulation templates run.\"}\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between\">\n            <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/30\">ENCLAVE DRY-RUNS</span>\n            <Link href=\"/build/sandbox\" className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-white hover:text-[#009DFF] transition flex items-center gap-1\">\n              <span>{workspace.sandbox ? \"RESUME\" : \"START\"}</span>\n              <span>→</span>\n            </Link>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Card 7: Marketplace Comparisons */}\n        <div className={`p-4 rounded-xl border flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[140px] transition-all ${workspace.marketplace?.compareIds?.length > 0 ? \"border-[#EC4899]/30 bg-[#EC4899]/5\" : \"border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01]\"}`}>\n          <div>\n            <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-2\">\n              <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold text-[#EC4899] uppercase\">7. Agent Marketplace</span>\n              <span className={`text-[8px] font-mono px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded ${workspace.marketplace?.compareIds?.length > 0 ? \"bg-[#EC4899]/20 text-white\" : \"bg-white/5 text-white/40\"}`}>\n                {workspace.marketplace?.compareIds?.length > 0 ? \"CONFIGURED\" : \"EMPTY\"}\n              </span>\n            </div>\n            <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white mt-3\">Model Comparisons</h4>\n            <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 font-light mt-1 min-h-[30px] line-clamp-2\">\n              {workspace.marketplace?.compareIds?.length > 0 ? `${workspace.marketplace.compareIds.length} sovereign agent configurations under comparison.` : \"No compared agent recipes.\"}\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between\">\n            <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/30\">RECIPES STACK</span>\n            <Link href=\"/build/marketplace\" className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-white hover:text-[#EC4899] transition flex items-center gap-1\">\n              <span>{workspace.marketplace?.compareIds?.length > 0 ? \"RESUME\" : \"START\"}</span>\n              <span>→</span>\n            </Link>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Card 8: Foundry Studio */}\n        <div className={`p-4 rounded-xl border flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[140px] transition-all ${workspace.foundryStudio ? \"border-[#00FF9D]/30 bg-[#00FF9D]/5\" : \"border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01]\"}`}>\n          <div>\n            <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-2\">\n              <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold text-[#00FF9D] uppercase\">8. Foundry Studio</span>\n              <span className={`text-[8px] font-mono px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded ${workspace.foundryStudio ? \"bg-[#00FF9D]/20 text-white\" : \"bg-white/5 text-white/40\"}`}>\n                {workspace.foundryStudio ? \"CONFIGURED\" : \"EMPTY\"}\n              </span>\n            </div>\n            <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white mt-3\">Custom Workflow DAG</h4>\n            <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 font-light mt-1 min-h-[30px] line-clamp-2\">\n              {workspace.foundryStudio ? `Active pattern: ${workspace.foundryStudio.selectedPattern}. Stages count: ${workspace.foundryStudio.stages?.length || 0}` : \"No customized multi-agent execution flows.\"}\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"mt-4 pt-3 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between\">\n            <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/30\">DAG COMPILING</span>\n            <Link href=\"/build/foundry-studio\" className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-white hover:text-[#00FF9D] transition flex items-center gap-1\">\n              <span>{workspace.foundryStudio ? \"RESUME\" : \"START\"}</span>\n              <span>→</span>\n            </Link>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  );\n}\n"}}}
